&quot;Kidnapping is a threat to the national security interests of the United States, and it must not be allowed to happen.&quot;
Whether Panetta&#39;s letter and recent warnings from senators will increase pressure for a budget compromise or intensify calls to exempt the Pentagon from cuts remains to be seen.
